# Node (if we add a build step later)
node_modules/
package-lock.json

# Processed data is regenerated by `scripts/preprocess.py` and
# `scripts/build_topojson.py`, but we commit the generated files so the
# site works immediately on clone (the Milestone 2 prototype + Milestone 3
# grading both assume `git clone && serve src/` is enough).
# Nothing to ignore here — kept as a reminder of the convention.

